FBIS4-36182 "drnes109_j_94035" FBIS-NES-94-109 Daily Report 4 Jun 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Deputy Finance Minister Appointed Deputy Finance Minister Appointed EA0406194394 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in Arabic 1700 GMT 4 Jun 94 EA0406194394 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in Arabic 1700 GMT 4 Jun 94 Arabic BFN [Text] Republican Decree No. 3 for 1994 was issued today. It concerned appointing a deputy finance minister. The first article states that Brother Muhammad Salih al-Wali has been appointed deputy finance minister. The second article states that the decree is effective from the date of its issuance and is to be published in the official gazette.
